"A.P.238/4/9/13:00": "Wow, not bad at all. You really put forth a lot of effort!"
"For you to be able to push me back like this, you really stand above the rest!"
"It took both of us all of our strength and you're so calmly..."
"Alright, that's enough! The important thing isn't winning or losing! I got a feeling for who you are!"
"...This guy isn't ordinary. There's two of us here."
"Well, I train pretty hard! But you also have considerable power!"
"If you keep on training, you'll probably surpass even me!"
"The exhibition match ends here! I have nothing but praise for you guys!"
"I only hope that this experience drives you to reach further heights! Farewell!"
"Hm? Do you have something to say other than congratulations?"
"I felt it when we crossed blades! You have a fine spirit! So the small details don't matter!"
"Keep justice in your heart, and things will work out alright! Don't worry about being a little reckless!"
"Was that all you wanted to ask? Well then!"
"...He's all kinds of unusual, that one. I see I've got a way to go yet."
"Well then, here we are. It was fun teaming up. See you around."
